  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the blood cultures' profitability in intensive care
      unit and create a validated prediction rule for extractioning in critical patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Implementing a predictive rule blood cultures to determine the probability of positive or
      negative result, improving the profitability of the diagnostic test.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
